<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3282855">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3282855/" class="title-link">丛书中的一本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3282855"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/claymoreteresa/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4316980-64.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/claymoreteresa/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">联合帝国</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-19"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-19 12:18:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3282855_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为南宋史研究丛书中的一本，该书对于南宋的军事制度、主要战争进程、武器装备、将领等等作了广泛的分析和叙述，并且用较大篇幅对南宋军事领域的几个特点：比如水军、山城防御体系等等进行了介绍，而这些是南宋赖以对抗北方游牧国家骑兵的重点。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3282855/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3282855_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3282855_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










